snippet: Sixth-seeded Federico Delbonis of Argentina beat Janko Tipsarevic 6-1, 7-6 (6) on the Serbian's return from an eight-month injury absence at the Geneva Open on Monday....
lead_paragraph: Sixth-seeded Federico Delbonis of Argentina beat Janko Tipsarevic 6-1, 7-6 (6) on the Serbian's return from an eight-month injury absence at the Geneva Open on Monday.

headline.print_headline: Delbonis Beats Fit-Again Tipsarevic in Geneva Open 1st Round
headline.main: Delbonis Beats Fit-Again Tipsarevic in Geneva Open 1st Round
